In the plugin org.eclipse.emf.workspace, version 1.0.2 of emft-transaction
org.eclipse.emf.workspace.util.WorkspaceSynchronizer.getFile() is called by most TransactionalCommand of GMF runtime.

All the commands that rely on this static method will fail when the Resource uses the "archive" scheme. In that case, the IFile is not resolved.

Support for the archive scheme consists of inserting:

